org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.processors

Class CommandProcessorResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Throwable
      • java.lang.Exception
        • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.processors.CommandProcessorResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class CommandProcessorResponse
extends Exception
    Encapsulates the basic response info returned by classes the implement the CommandProcessor interface. Typically errorMessage and SQLState will only be set if the responseCode is not 0. Note that often responseCode ends up the exit value of command shell process so should keep it to < 127.
